  "notes": "Its full-speed ADS behaviour comes from having no scope part at all (NULL) rather than the usual Scope_None; forcing NULL on other guns produces the same effect. Only Greed and the Interfacer can spawn with this setup. With enough Expertise (and skill-boosting class mods), a Commando can move extremely fast while aiming. It can be repeatedly farmed by re-entering The Leviathan's Lair and using co-op join/respawn tricks to spawn inside the Leviathan, then killing Roscoe; save-quit returns you inside for another run.",
